---
title: Pesto Pomodoro Pasta with cherry tomatoes and Italian cheese
description: Cherry tomatoes form the base of the creamy pomodoro sauce coating the linguine in this Italian-inspired dish. Continuing the Mediterranean theme are gorgeous green pesto and grated Italian style cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230112_R08_W10_IE_IECFQVV13681-2_Main_high-c4a53806.jpg
